author: Kotte Animation
description:
The battle for the fate of the Demon Slayer Corps has begun in the Infinity Castle!
Wait — is that Upper Rank Three, Akaza?!
But something seems to be wrong with him...
Can Tanjiro defeat him?

I actually had no plan to extend after the shorts version, but then thought I can make this one real quick. But then the demonetization thing happened, and this took too long! Sorry guys!
